<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
     <meta charset="utf-8">
     <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
     <style>
          body {
               font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
               line-height: 1.4;
               color: #333;
               max-width: 800px;
               margin: 0 auto;
               padding: 40px 20px;
          }

          .header {
               border-bottom: 2px solid #f97316;
               padding-bottom: 20px;
               margin-bottom: 30px;
               display: flex;
               justify-content: space-between;
               align-items: center;
          }

          .logo {
               max-width: 150px;
          }

          .booking-ref {
               text-align: right;
               color: #666;
          }

          .booking-ref span {
               color: #f97316;
               font-weight: bold;
          }

          .grid-container {
               display: grid;
               grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
               gap: 30px;
               margin-bottom: 30px;
          }

          .section {
               margin-bottom: 20px;
          }

          .section h2 {
               color: #f97316;
               font-size: 18px;
               margin: 0 0 15px 0;
               padding-bottom: 8px;
               border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
          }

          .info-grid {
               display: grid;
               grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
               gap: 8px 15px;
          }

          .label {
               font-weight: bold;
               color: #666;
          }

          .value {
               color: #333;
          }

          .pricing-note {
               background-color: #fff9f5;
               border: 1px solid #f97316;
               padding: 15px;
               margin: 20px 0;
               color: #666;
          }

          .pricing-note h3 {
               color: #f97316;
               margin: 0 0 10px 0;
               font-size: 16px;
          }

          .pricing-note ul {
               margin: 0;
               padding-left: 20px;
          }

          .footer {
               margin-top: 40px;
               padding-top: 20px;
               border-top: 1px solid #eee;
               text-align: center;
               font-size: 12px;
               color: #666;
          }

          .contact {
               color: #f97316;
               font-weight: bold;
               text-decoration: none;
          }
     </style>
</head>

<body>
     <div class="header">
          <img src="<%= process.env.BASE_URL %>/images/logo.png" alt="Morocco Travel Experts" class="logo">
          <div class="booking-ref">
               <p>Booking Reference:<br><span><%= booking._id %></span></p>
               <p>Date: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></p>
          </div>
     </div>

     <div class="grid-container">
          <div class="section">
               <h2>Tour Details</h2>
               <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="label">Tour Name:</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= booking.tour.title %></div>
                    
                    <div class="label">Duration:</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= booking.tour.duration %> days</div>
                    
                    <div class="label">Start Location:</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= booking.tour.startLocation %></div>
                    
                    <div class="label">Tour Date:</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= new Date(booking.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></div>
               </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section">
               <h2>Customer Information</h2>
               <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="label">Name:</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= booking.firstName %> <%= booking.lastName %></div>
                    
                    <div class="label">Email:</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= booking.email %></div>
                    
                    <div class="label">Group Size:</div>
                    <div class="value"><%= booking.groupSize %> people</div>
                    
                    <div class="label">Status:</div>
                    <div class="value">Pending Confirmation</div>
               </div>
          </div>
     </div>

     <div class="pricing-note">
          <h3>Pricing Information</h3>
          <p>We offer personalized pricing based on group size, season, accommodation preferences, and additional services. Our team will contact you shortly with a detailed quote tailored to your requirements.</p>
          <ul>
               <li>Customized pricing for your group of <%= booking.groupSize %> people</li>
               <li>Flexible payment options available</li>
               <li>Special rates for early bookings</li>
          </ul>
     </div>

     <div class="footer">
          <p>Thank you for choosing Morocco Travel Experts for your adventure!</p>
          <p>For any inquiries, please contact us at <span class="contact">contact@moroccotravelexperts.com</span></p>
          <p>Morocco Travel Experts - Your Gateway to Authentic Moroccan Experiences</p>
     </div>
</body>

</html>